data.description: VA ASSUMABLE RATE OF 2.875%! Incredible rancher farmhouse with full basement, located on 18+ acres with room for everything; cattle, horses, farm living, man cave, shooting range, 11x17 walk-in vault, even a place to land a chopper in the back pasture. This home features beautiful kitchen with double ovens & stainless-steel refrigerator that conveys. Enjoy your mornings sitting on the 432 sq ft enclosed back porch overlooking your beautiful property. The walk-out basement includes a bathroom & is perfect for entertaining. There are too many amenities to list. The home is located on a private dead-end road. This is truly a one-of-a-kind listing. Only forty-five minutes from Research Park.
